titles.title: I will come / We will come

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
C
I will come and bow down at your feet Lord Jesus
In your presence is fullness of joy
There is nothing - There is no one
Who compares with you
I take pleasure in worshiping you Lord

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
We will come and bow down at your feet Lord Jesus
In your presence is fullness of joy
There is nothing - There is no one
Who compares with you
We take pleasure in worshiping you Lord
